descript.purpose: This data is intended for basic mapping and represenational needs. It is not intended for high accuracy & precision uses, such as engineering applications. This data includes mostly UofM owned buildings, but also includes some are building footprints for buildings not owned by the UofM. Generally, a building with a building number in the attributes table is UofM owned.
